	Here are some documents on the picture widget.

	The contents of each file is as follows:

==> coordinates <==

	Some explanation about the coordinates.

==> file_format <==

	Some explanation about the picture file format.

==> makefile <==

	Can be used to print out the 'picture.n' file.

==> picture.n <==

	MAN pages for the picture widget.
	This file is in troff format, and includes some pic and tbl commands.

==> text <==

	Some supplementary explanation for the text primitive.
